{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "8b5f39c2-5b94-4d89-a21c-5509a25b3fa2",
    "name": "Smart City Integrated Platform",
    "description": "Super Complete API Collection untuk Smart City Integrated Platform: Gateway, OAuth 2.0 (Password, Client Credentials, Refresh Token, Introspect, Revoke), Citizen, Power, Grid, dan ML Service.\n\nDisesuaikan dengan kondisi repo terbaru (proxy gateway sudah memakai pathRewrite + fixRequestBody, login warga memverifikasi password ber-hash bcrypt, refresh_token grant sudah berfungsi).\n\nFITUR OTOMATIS:\n- Setiap request login (Password Grant Warga/Admin, Client Credentials) otomatis menyimpan access_token & refresh_token ke collection variable lewat Tests script.\n- Pre-request Script di level COLLECTION (bukan per-request) otomatis memeriksa apakah token sudah/akan kedaluwarsa sebelum SETIAP request lain dikirim, dan kalau iya, otomatis memanggil grant_type=refresh_token lebih dulu tanpa perlu login ulang manual.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "prerequest",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "// ============================================================================",
          "// AUTO-REFRESH TOKEN — jalan otomatis SEBELUM setiap request di collection ini.",
          "// Kalau access token (warga/admin/service) sudah/akan kedaluwarsa, script ini",
          "// memanggil grant_type=refresh_token ke gateway terlebih dahulu dan menyimpan",
          "// token baru ke collection variable, sebelum request aslinya benar-benar dikirim.",
          "// ============================================================================",
          "",
          "const AUTH_PATHS = [\"/oauth/token\", \"/oauth/introspect\", \"/oauth/revoke\"];",
          "const currentUrl = pm.request.url.toString();",
          "const isAuthRequest = AUTH_PATHS.some(function (p) { return currentUrl.indexOf(p) !== -1; });",
          "",
          "if (!isAuthRequest) {",
          "    refreshIfNeeded(\"ACCESS_TOKEN\", \"REFRESH_TOKEN\", \"TOKEN_EXPIRES_AT\", pm.collectionVariables.get(\"CLIENT_ID\"), pm.collectionVariables.get(\"CLIENT_SECRET\"));",
          "    refreshIfNeeded(\"ADMIN_TOKEN\", \"ADMIN_REFRESH_TOKEN\", \"ADMIN_TOKEN_EXPIRES_AT\", pm.collectionVariables.get(\"ADMIN_CLIENT_ID\"), pm.collectionVariables.get(\"CLIENT_SECRET\"));",
          "    refreshIfNeeded(\"SERVICE_TOKEN\", \"SERVICE_REFRESH_TOKEN\", \"SERVICE_TOKEN_EXPIRES_AT\", pm.collectionVariables.get(\"IOT_CLIENT_ID\"), pm.collectionVariables.get(\"IOT_CLIENT_SECRET\"));",
          "}",
          "",
          "function refreshIfNeeded(accessKey, refreshKey, expiryKey, clientId, clientSecret) {",
          "    const refreshToken = pm.collectionVariables.get(refreshKey);",
          "    const expiresAt = parseInt(pm.collectionVariables.get(expiryKey) || \"0\", 10);",
          "    const BUFFER_MS = 15000; // refresh 15 detik sebelum benar-benar expired",
          "",
          "    if (!refreshToken) return; // belum pernah login lewat flow ini, biarkan apa adanya",
          "    if (Date.now() < expiresAt - BUFFER_MS) return; // token masih cukup valid, tidak perlu refresh",
          "",
          "    const gatewayUrl = pm.collectionVariables.get(\"GATEWAY_URL\");",
          "",
          "    pm.sendRequest({",
          "        url: gatewayUrl + \"/oauth/token\",",
          "        method: \"POST\",",
          "        header: { \"Content-Type\": \"application/json\" },",
          "        body: {",
          "            mode: \"raw\",",
          "            raw: JSON.stringify({",
          "                grant_type: \"refresh_token\",",
          "                refresh_token: refreshToken,",
          "                client_id: clientId,",
          "                client_secret: clientSecret",
          "            })",
          "        }",
          "    }, function (err, res) {",
          "        if (err) {",
          "            console.error(\"\\u274c Auto-refresh \" + accessKey + \" gagal (network):\", err);",
          "            return;",
          "        }",
          "        let json;",
          "        try { json = res.json(); } catch (e) { json = null; }",
          "",
          "        if (json && json.status === \"success\" && json.data && json.data.access_token) {",
          "            pm.collectionVariables.set(accessKey, json.data.access_token);",
          "            pm.collectionVariables.set(refreshKey, json.data.refresh_token);",
          "            pm.collectionVariables.set(expiryKey, String(Date.now() + (json.data.expires_in * 1000)));",
          "            console.log(\"\\ud83d\\udd04 \" + accessKey + \" berhasil di-refresh otomatis.\");",
          "        } else {",
          "            console.warn(\"\\u26a0\\ufe0f Auto-refresh \" + accessKey + \" ditolak server (refresh token mungkin sudah kedaluwarsa). Silakan login ulang manual.\", json);",
          "        }",
          "    });",
          "}"
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
